text.section:
If a bail bondsman arranges to accept payment for the premium charged for a bail bond in installments, the installment agreement shall include:
the total amount of the premium owed;
the amount of any down payment made;
the balance amount owed to the bail bondsman or the bail bondsman's insurer;
the amount and due date of each installment payment; and
the total number of installment payments required to pay the amount due.
